<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV28">
<l>taṇṇan tuḻāyvaḷai koḷvati yāmiḻap pōnaṭuvē</l>
<l>vaṇṇan tuḻāviyōr vāṭai yulāvumvaḷ vāyalakāṟ</l>
<l>puṇṇan tuḻāmē porunīrt tiruvaraṅ kāvaruḷā</l>
<l>yeṇṇan tuḻāvu miṭattuḷa vōpaṇṭu miṉṉaṉṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The cool Tulsi takes [our] bangles. In the middle of our loosing [them]</l>
<l>a north wind wanders, groping for [our] colour. You of Tiruvaraṅkam</l>
<l>with waters dashing so that birds with sharp-tipped beaks don’t plough for conches,</l>
<l>you are not gracious: upon thought, have things ever been like that before?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
